body.description: Clorox Disinfecting Wipes clean, disinfect, deodorize and remove allergens for 5x cleaning power* and leave a pleasant scent. Disinfecting Wipes clean and disinfect with antibacterial power that kills 99.9% of viruses and bacteria that can live on surfaces, including COVID-19* Virus, staph, E. coli, MRSA, salmonella, strep and Kleb. These all-purpose disposable wipes remove common allergens, germs and messes on surfaces like kitchen counters, bathroom surfaces and more and can prevent the growth of bacteria* for up to 24 hours. Wipes are safe to use on finished wood, sealed granite and stainless steel. Clean with bleach-free wipes to keep dirt and germs away. Do not flush. *5x cleaning power: cleans, disinfects, deodorizes, removes allergens, leaves a scent, removes dirt, removes grime. Kills COVID-19 virus: kills SARS-CoV-2 on hard, nonporous surfaces. Use as directed. Prevents the growth of bacteria: odor causing bacteria on non-food contact surfaces. Allow product to air dry.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It Saved My Life: Clorox Disinfecting Wipes, Bleach-Free Cleaning Wipes
reviews.reviewText: Prepare yourself for a tale of survival, triumph, and a true hero in my life - the Clorox Disinfecting Wipes! Let me tell you, these bleach-free cleaning wipes have transformed my world, and I can confidently say that they saved my life.In these uncertain times, hygiene and cleanliness have become paramount. Like many, I found myself grappling with the constant worry of germs lurking on every surface, endangering my health and the well-being of my loved ones. I needed a solution, and it arrived in the form of these magical multi-surface wipes from Clorox.From the moment I opened the container, a pleasant fresh scent engulfed my senses, immediately instilling a sense of comfort and assurance that my surroundings were about to undergo a transformation. These wipes were not just ordinary cleaning tools; they were my ultimate weapon against invisible foes.The first battlefield was my kitchen, a breeding ground for potential contaminants. Armed with Clorox Disinfecting Wipes, I waged war against grime, grease, and germs with ease. Countertops, stovetops, and appliance surfaces surrendered under the might of these wipes, leaving behind nothing but a pristine shine and the sweet scent of victory.But it didn't end there. My bathroom, notorious for hosting an array of bacteria, met its match when I wielded these bleach-free warriors. Mirrors, tiles, and faucets gleamed as if they were brand new. No soap scum or water stains were safe, and my bathroom transformed into a sanctuary of cleanliness and tranquility.Beyond my home, these wipes proved invaluable during my travels. Whether I was venturing through public spaces, hotel rooms, or transportation, the Clorox Disinfecting Wipes stood strong as my first line of defense. Armed with their power, I wiped down airplane seats, hotel room doorknobs, and restaurant tables, allowing me to explore with peace of mind.In the darkest days of the pandemic, when the world seemed to be consumed by fear and uncertainty, Clorox Disinfecting Wipes brought light into my life. Their presence was a constant source of reassurance and hope, reminding me that there was something I could do to protect myself and those around me.I must commend Clorox for creating a product that goes beyond mere cleaning. These wipes are symbols of resilience, strength, and adaptability. They symbolize the power of taking charge of one's environment and staying safe amidst the storm.In conclusion, Clorox Disinfecting Wipes, Bleach-Free Cleaning Wipes, with their fresh scent and extraordinary germ-fighting capabilities, have undoubtedly saved my life. They have been my trusty companions in the battle against unseen adversaries, transforming my surroundings into havens of cleanliness and health.To anyone seeking an epic ally in the fight for cleanliness and safety, I wholeheartedly recommend Clorox Disinfecting Wipes. Embrace them, and you too will experience the joy of victory over dirt and germs. Thank you, Clorox, for being the beacon of hope in these challenging times!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Makes cleaning extremely convenient
reviews.reviewText: Wipes perforated, lid holds wipes in place for easy dispensing, extra liquid in the bottom to keep wipes moist for extended shelf life, what more can I ask. Definitely takes the extra step of getting a washcloth and putting soap and disinfectant on it out before beginning to clean. In other words, I can just whip it out and I’m ready, which saves some time. Even the extra liquid comes in handy if I already ran out of the wipes themselves, I could put a couple of wash clothes in there so it doesn’t go to waste. It can all be used! And even the smell of it is not too overpowering, the citrus smell of it makes it easier on my nose when I’m cleaning.
